nodes.text: Laine Liska is a makeup artist who worked on Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope. Liska and Rick Baker designed masks for aliens in the movie's Mos Eisley cantina scene. His contributions include the masks of Muftak, Hem Dazon, Myo, and Feltipern Trevagg. Liska also portrayed the characters Muftak and Nalan Cheel in the cantina scene.
